com.soa.rs.discordbot.cfg

Class DiscordCfg

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soa.rs.discordbot.cfg.DiscordCfg

  • public class DiscordCfg
extends Object
    The DiscordCfg singleton class is used for storing any configuration which will be accessed by other parts of the bot. Configuration can be stored within this class for easy access from other classes as needed.
